  "synopsis": "Comical adventure story starring Kasukabe Defense Forces and dealing with \"food\" as theme. Kasukabe Defense Forces (Shinnosuke and his mates: Kazama-kun, Nene-chan, Masao-kun and Bo-chan) decide to attend \"B-class Gourmet Carnival\", a big event in Kasukabe, without their parents, to eat very tasty yakisoba sauce cooked by \"Sauce's Ken\". On the way, a mystery woman asks them to bring a legendary sauce to Sauce's Ken. They head to the event site with the sauce, but they wander off into a mountain, and \"A-class Gourmet Organization\", an organization plotting to eliminate B-class gourmet, seeks to take the sauce away from them.\n\n(Source: Manabu Tsuribe)",
